{"tid":1829994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禾輋廣場美心遭刑毁","createTime":"2020-01-19T09:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T14:26:13.000Z","uid":51271,"like":834,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"94cc7cb92429245a80b1d7fedf0bd8ac3b3d6414","tid":1829994,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:02:42.000Z","msg":"中午近1時，警方接報，獲悉有黑衣人持槌闖入沙田禾輋廣場一間美心快餐店，毁壞上址玻璃及收銀機，事後逃逸。警方事後到場調查，將案件列作刑事毁壞處理。涉事美心事後下半閘暫停營業。記者在現場觀察，未見嚴重損毁，快餐店大門部分位置有圍板遮蓋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200119/s00001/5fd7c458d8021b1214c20d33497636a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200119%2Fs00001%2F5fd7c458d8021b1214c20d33497636a7.jpg&h=381bb539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200119/s00001/1579420304043/%e7%a6%be%e8%bc%8b%e5%bb%a3%e5%a0%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%bf%83%e9%81%ad%e5%88%91%e6%af%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200119%2Fs00001%2F1579420304043%2F%25e7%25a6%25be%25e8%25bc%258b%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25bf%2583%25e9%2581%25ad%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%25af%2581&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1PUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e848e642\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200119%2Fs00001%2F1579420304043%2F%25e7%25a6%25be%25e8%25bc%258b%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25bf%2583%25e9%2581%25ad%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%25af%2581&h=f4cbac17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200119/s00001/1579420304043/%e7%a6%be%e8%bc%8b%e5%bb%a3%e5%a0%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%bf%83%e9%81%ad%e5%88%91%e6%af%81</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今日太大風了</strong>"},{"pid":"9e595033d002d33570385209c7dfce8ce8adffa2","tid":1829994,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited